\c 22
\s UPawuli ulandisela amaJuda ngokuphenduka kwakhe
\p
\v 1 Madoda, bazalwane, labobaba, zwanini ukuziphendulela kwami khathesi kini\x + 7.2.\x*.
\v 2 Sebezwile ukuthi ukhuluma labo ngolimi lwamaHebheru, bathula kakhulu\x + 21.40.\x*, wasesithi:
\v 3 Mina ngiyindoda engumJuda\x + Roma 11.1. 2 Kor. 11.22. Fil. 3.5. Seb. 21.39.\x*, eyazalelwa eTarsu yeKilikhiya, ngakhuliselwa kulumuzi\x + 2 Kho. 4.38.\x* enyaweni zikaGamaliyeli\x + 5.34.\x*, ngafundiswa ngokuqinileyo umlayo wabobaba\x + 26.5.\x*, ngitshisekela uNkulunkulu\x + 21.20.\x*, njengani lonke lamuhla\x + Roma 10.2.\x*;
\v 4 eyazingela leyondlela\x + 21.19. 8.3.\x* kwaze kwaba sekufeni, ngi\add ba\add*bopha ngi\add ba\add*nikela entolongweni amadoda kanye labafazi\x + 9.2.\x*,
\v 5 njengoba lompristi omkhulu engifakazela, lomphakathi wonke wabadala\x + Luka 22.66.\x*; engazuza kubo incwadi eziya kubazalwane\x + 9.2. 26.10,11.\x*, ngaya eDamaseko, ukuthi lababekhona lapho ngibalethe eJerusalema bebotshiwe, ukuze bajeziswe.
\v 6 Kwasekusithi ngisahamba sengisondela eDamaseko, sekungaba yimini enkulu, kwahle kwakhanya ukukhanya okukhulu okuvela ezulwini kungizingelezela.
\v 7 Ngasengiwela phansi, ngasengisizwa ilizwi lisithi kimi: Sawuli, Sawuli, ungizingelelani?
\v 8 Mina ngasengiphendula \add ngathi\add*: Ungubani, Nkosi? Wasesithi kimi: NginguJesu weNazaretha wena omzingelayo\x + 9.3-8. 26.12-18.\x*.
\v 9 Lalabo ababelami bakubona ukukhanya, njalo basebesesaba, kodwa kabalizwanga ilizwi elakhuluma lami\x + Joha. 8.43.\x*.
\v 10 Ngasengisithi: Ngenzeni, Nkosi? INkosi yasisithi kimi: Sukuma uye eDamaseko; njalo uzatshelwa khona ngazo zonke izinto ozimiselwe ukuthi uzenze.
\v 11 Njengoba ngangingaboni ngenxa yenkazimulo yalokhokukhanya, ngakhokhelwa ngesandla yilabo ababelami, ngafika eDamaseko.
\v 12 Njalo uAnaniya othile\x + 9.10.\x*, indoda ekhuthele ekukhonzeni ngokomlayo\x + 10.2.\x*, owayefakazelwa yiwo wonke amaJuda ahlala \add khona\x + 6.3.\x*\add*,
\v 13 weza kimi wasesima phansi kwami\x + 9.17,18.\x* wathi kimi: Sawuli mzalwane, buya ubone. Njalo mina ngalesosikhathi ngasengimbona.
\v 14 Wasesithi: UNkulunkulu wabobaba bethu\x + 3.13. 5.30.\x* ukumisile ngaphambili\x + 26.16.\x* ukuthi wazi intando yakhe\x + Joha. 7.17.\x*, lokuthi ubone\x + 22.18.23.11. 1 Kor. 9.1.15.8.\x* oLungileyo\x + 3.14.\x*, njalo uzwe ilizwi eliphuma emlonyeni wakhe\x + 1 Kor. 11.23. Gal. 1.12.\x*,
\v 15 ngoba uzakuba ngumfakazi wakhe\x + 26.16.\x* kubo bonke abantu\x + 23.11.\x*, walokho okubonileyo lokuzwileyo\x + 26.16.\x*.
\v 16 Khathesi-ke, usalindeleni? Sukuma ubhabhathizwe\x + 9.18.\x* uhlanjululwe ezonweni zakho\x + Hlab. 51.2. Heb. 10.22. Seb. 2.38.\x*, ubize ibizo leNkosi\x + 9.14.\x*.
\v 17 Kwasekusithi kimi sengibuyele eJerusalema\x + 9.26. 2 Kor. 12.2.\x*, njalo ngikhuleka ethempelini, ngaba lokuhlehla kwengqondo\x + 10.10. 11.5. 2 Kor. 12.1-4.\x*,
\v 18 ngasengimbona wathi kimi: Phangisa uphume ngesiqubu eJerusalema\x + 22.14.\x*; ngoba kabasoze bemukele ubufakazi bakho ngami\x + 9.29.\x*.
\v 19 Ngasengisithi: Nkosi, bayazi bona ukuthi mina ngangibafaka entolongweni\x + 22.4.\x* ngibatshaya emasinagogeni wonke labo abakholwa kuwe\x + 26.11. Mat. 10.17.\x*;
\v 20 njalo mhla kuchithwa igazi likaStefane umfakazi wakho\x + Isam. 2.13.\x*, mina uqobo ngangimi khona ngivumelana lokufa kwakhe\x + 8.1. Roma 1.32. Seb. 26.10.\x*, njalo ngilondoloza izembatho zalabo abambulalayo\x + 7.58.\x*.
\v 21 Wasesithi kimi: Hamba, ngoba mina ngizakuthuma\x + 26.17. 9.15. 28.28.\x* khatshana kwabezizwe\x + 2.39.\x*.
\s AmaJuda afuna ukubulala uPawuli
\p
\v 22 Bamlalela kwaze kwafika kulelolizwi, baphakamisa ilizwi labo\x + Luka 11.27.\x* besithi: Msuseni onje emhlabeni\x + 21.36.\x*, ngoba kakufanele ukuthi aphile\x + 25.24.\x*!
\v 23 Kwathi besamemeza, baphosa izembatho, baphosa uthuli emoyeni,
\v 24 induna enkulu yalaya ukuthi angeniswe enkambeni yamabutho\x + 21.34.\x*, yathi kahlolisiswe ngokutshaywa ngesiswepu\x + 22.29.\x*, ukuze yazi ukuthi kungasizatho bani bememeza ngokunjalo ngaye.
\v 25 Kwathi sebemelulele phambili ngemichilo, uPawuli wathi enduneni yekhulu eyayimi lapho: Kuvunyelwe kini yini ukutshaya ngesiswepu umuntu ongumRoma\x + 16.37.\x* engalahlwanga licala\x + 16.37.\x*?
\v 26 Induna yekhulu isizwile yasondela yatshela induna enkulu isithi: Nanzelela osuzakwenza; ngoba lumuntu ungumRoma.
\v 27 Induna enkulu yasifika yathi kuye: Ngitshele, wena ungumRoma yini? Yena wathi: Yebo.
\v 28 Induna enkulu yasiphendula \add yathi\add*: Mina lelilungelo lokuba yisakhamuzi ngalizuza ngemali enkulu\x + Mat. 10.9.\x*. UPawuli wasesithi: Kodwa lami ngazalwa \add lalo\add*.
\v 29 Ngakho labo abasebezamhlola bahle basuka kuye. Lenduna enkulu layo yesaba, isisazi ukuthi ungumRoma, lokuthi ibimbophile\x + 16.3.\x*.
\p
\v 30 Kwathi kusisa ifuna ukwazi iqiniso, ukuthi kungani emangalelwa ngamaJuda, yamkhulula kuzibopho\x + 26.29. 21.33. 28.20.\x*, yalaya ukuthi abapristi abakhulu lomphakathi wabo wonke babuye\x + 23.1,6,15,20,28. 24.20. Mat. 5.22.\x*, yamehlisa uPawuli ya\add m\add*misa phambi kwabo\x + 21.35. 23.10,15,28.\x*.